file.string: Hide word suggestions in landscape view
Capitalize the start of a sentence
Spacebar and punctuation automatically insert highlighted word
Hold a key down to see accents (ø, ö, etc.)
Press the back key \u21B6 to close the keyboard at any point
Press and hold the left-most word to add it to the dictionary
Touch here to close this hint and start typing!

string.name: tip_to_open_keyboard
string.b: The keyboard opens any time you touch a text field

string.name: tip_to_view_accents
string.b: Touch & hold a key to view accents\n(ø, ö, ô, ó, and so on)

string.name: tip_to_open_symbols
string.b: Switch to numbers and symbols by touching this key

string.name: tip_to_close_symbols
string.b: Go back to letters by touching this key again

string.name: tip_to_launch_settings
string.b: Touch & hold this key to change keyboard settings, like auto complete

string.name: tip_to_start_typing
string.b: Try it!
